#### Docker Container



#### act

For testing the GitHub Actions workflow locally before pushing it.

1. Install act and check if it worked

    ```
    curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nektos/act/master/install.sh | sudo bash
    ```
    ```
    act --version
    ```

2. Run act

    ```
    act -v -j <job-name> -P ubuntu-latest=ghcr.io/catthehacker/ubuntu:act-latest
    ```

    Notes:
    - `-P ubuntu-latest=ghcr.io/catthehacker/ubuntu:act-latest`: choose the medium image
    - `-v`: show verbose logs